snippet.title: Range is HOT! Rifle Walkthrough
snippet.description:
In this video we explain the functionality of the Rifle in our game "Range is HOT". Lots of cool interactive parts that we are still tweaking to get the most realistic feel. 

Check out Range is HOT! Available on Steam Early Access March 9th 2021. 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1503590/Range_is_HOT/
